      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Esecuzione open output                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "OO"                 to   g-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mlsfil"
                                         using g                      .
